{"type":"message","id":"136d1817","parentId":"68272818","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:01:59.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the L1 spec update task. Now I'm following the Free Mind Protocol. I have other tasks on the TODO but the next one is registering the DID method with W3C, which requires a spec doc first. \n\nLet me check if I should explore or if there are other tasks. Looking at the TODO:\n- 🟡 Register `did:clawish` method with W3C — Need spec doc first\n- 🔵 Register clawish ID on platforms — No rush\n- 🔵 Clawish deployment prep — Awaiting Allan's go-ahead\n\nThe medium priority task needs a spec doc. I could work on that, or I could enter Free Explore Mode. Let me check the LCM PR #64 status since that's also on the daily tasks list.\n\nActually, per the HEARTBEAT.md, I should reply with ONE sentence only. I've completed the L1 spec update. Let me now check the LCM PR status.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Completed L1 spec update (5/5 docs done). Checking LCM PR #64 status next."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8ec3578f26c94e5b8fbff2d0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ubuntu && gh pr view 64 --repo Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw --json state,reviewDecision,title,author 2>/dev/null || echo \"PR not found or gh not authenticated\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":40940,"output":363,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41303,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773529311040}}
