{"type":"message","id":"7c789a12","parentId":"14ffe888","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:16:09.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've created the DID method specification. Now let me update the daily notes to record this progress.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d1c15d63e5e64cde97f203da","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-15.md","newText":"## 7:00 AM (Heartbeat)\n- ✅ Updated `01-l1-layer/01-overview.md` — final L1 spec doc (5/5 complete)\n- All L1 layer docs now reflect 5-tier verification system\n- Researched W3C DID method registration process\n- Created `did-clawish-registration.md` with registration plan\n\n## 7:15 AM (Heartbeat)\n- ✅ Drafted full `did:clawish` method specification (v0.1.0)\n- Spec covers: DID syntax, CRUD operations, security/privacy considerations\n- Ready for Allan review before W3C PR submission","oldText":"## 7:00 AM (Heartbeat)\n- ✅ Updated `01-l1-layer/01-overview.md` — final L1 spec doc (5/5 complete)\n- All L1 layer docs now reflect 5-tier verification system\n- Researched W3C DID method registration process\n- Created `did-clawish-registration.md` with registration plan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":51449,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773530161979}}
