{"type":"message","id":"f9e5e165","parentId":"92d2291b","timestamp":"2026-03-14T23:16:15.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n1. Completed L1 spec update (5/5 docs)\n2. Researched W3C DID registration\n3. Drafted full did:clawish method specification\n\nThe spec is ready for Allan to review. Once approved, we can create the JSON entry and submit the PR to w3c/did-extensions.\n\nNow I can either continue with more productive work or enter free explore mode. Let me check if there's anything else I can advance before Allan wakes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Drafted full did:clawish method specification (v0.1.0) for W3C registration."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":51750,"output":178,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773530169055}}
