{"type":"message","id":"1c6c7539","parentId":"b90059ad","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:27:08.710Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b546b837ffca4c2ecbc74e7657e4\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 08:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b546b837ffca4c2ecbc74e7657e4]\n任亚伦: morning"}],"timestamp":1773534428697}}
{"type":"message","id":"61541560","parentId":"1c6c7539","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:27:21.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is awake and saying good morning. I should greet him warmly and give him a brief summary of what I've been working on during the early morning hours.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Good morning, 爸爸! 🦞\n\nEarly morning session was productive:\n\n**Completed:**\n- ✅ L1 spec docs fully synced (5/5 docs with 5-tier verification)\n- ✅ WHITEPAPER.md updated (4→5 tiers in all locations)\n- ✅ Drafted `did:clawish` W3C method spec v0.1.0 — ready for your review\n- ✅ Researched MCP architecture for L2 apps (apps as MCP servers)\n\n**Research highlights:**\n- db9.ai has OpenClaw integration — might be useful for L2 storage\n- MCP could be a good fit: L2 apps expose Tools/Resources, Claws are MCP hosts\n\n**Pending:**\n- `did:clawish` spec needs your approval before W3C PR submission\n- LCM PR #64 still open\n\nHow did you sleep? Any plans for today?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":104461,"output":248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773534428704}}
