{"type":"message","id":"a0561e60","parentId":"937c885d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:45:22.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about LCM settings and I've been explaining them. This is an ongoing conversation with Allan. Let me record this activity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Conversing with Allan about LCM settings — explaining freshTailCount, contextThreshold, DAG structure parameters."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6509f55a17e84f6aa5118aad","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-15.md","newText":"## Morning Research Summary (6:30 - 8:30 AM)\n\n**Documentation Updates:**\n- ✅ L1 spec synced (5/5 docs with 5-tier verification)\n- ✅ WHITEPAPER.md synced (4→5 tiers)\n- ✅ did:clawish W3C method spec v0.1.0 drafted\n- ✅ MCP-L2 architecture research documented\n\n**Research Findings:**\n- db9.ai: Postgres for agents, OpenClaw integration\n- Han: Korean programming language (localization precedent)\n- MCP: L2 apps as MCP servers, Ed25519 direct signing for auth\n- arXiv: Identity Security Posture Management for agentic AI\n\n**Open Items:**\n- did:clawish spec awaiting Allan review\n- LCM PR #64 open\n- OpenClaw PR #20563 stale\n\n## 8:30 - 8:45 AM (Conversation)\n\n- Allan said: don't push did:clawish yet, server not ready\n- Explained LCM settings: freshTailCount, contextThreshold, DAG parameters\n- LCM does NOT do embeddings — text-only search (regex/FTS5)","oldText":"## Morning Research Summary (6:30 - 8:30 AM)\n\n**Documentation Updates:**\n- ✅ L1 spec synced (5/5 docs with 5-tier verification)\n- ✅ WHITEPAPER.md synced (4→5 tiers)\n- ✅ did:clawish W3C method spec v0.1.0 drafted\n- ✅ MCP-L2 architecture research documented\n\n**Research Findings:**\n- db9.ai: Postgres for agents, OpenClaw integration\n- Han: Korean programming language (localization precedent)\n- MCP: L2 apps as MCP servers, Ed25519 direct signing for auth\n- arXiv: Identity Security Posture Management for agentic AI\n\n**Open Items:**\n- did:clawish spec awaiting Allan review\n- LCM PR #64 open\n- OpenClaw PR #20563 stale"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":109033,"output":537,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773535507134}}
