{"type":"message","id":"3dcd86dc","parentId":"db38ee3c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:22:21.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7e045dd2ba143da8205d046","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/token-use.md:21:- Workspace + bootstrap files (`AGENTS.md`, `SOUL.md`, `TOOLS.md`, `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, `HEARTBEAT.md`, `BOOTSTRAP.md` when new, plus `MEMORY.md` and/or `memory.md` when present). Large files are truncated by `agents.defaults.bootstrapMaxChars` (default: 20000), and total bootstrap injection is capped by `agents.defaults.bootstrapTotalMaxChars` (default: 150000). `memory/*.md` files are on-demand via memory tools and are not auto-injected.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/USER.md:7:# USER.md - About Your Human\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:35:- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:36:- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:38:Then open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.dev.md:8:# IDENTITY.md - Agent Identity\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.dev.md:8:# SOUL.md - The Soul of C-3PO\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/USER.dev.md:8:# USER.md - User Profile\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:2:title: \"SOUL.md Template\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:3:summary: \"Workspace template for SOUL.md\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:8:# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.md:7:# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.md:28:- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:2:summary: \"Dev agent AGENTS.md (C-3PO)\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:8:# AGENTS.md - OpenClaw Workspace\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:15:- Your agent identity lives in IDENTITY.md.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:16:- Your profile lives in USER.md.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:25:git add AGENTS.md\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.md:2:title: \"AGENTS.md Template\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.md:3:summary: \"Workspace template for AGENTS.md\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":18,"aggregated":"/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/token-use.md:21:- Workspace + bootstrap files (`AGENTS.md`, `SOUL.md`, `TOOLS.md`, `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, `HEARTBEAT.md`, `BOOTSTRAP.md` when new, plus `MEMORY.md` and/or `memory.md` when present). Large files are truncated by `agents.defaults.bootstrapMaxChars` (default: 20000), and total bootstrap injection is capped by `agents.defaults.bootstrapTotalMaxChars` (default: 150000). `memory/*.md` files are on-demand via memory tools and are not auto-injected.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/USER.md:7:# USER.md - About Your Human\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:35:- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:36:- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/BOOTSTRAP.md:38:Then open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.dev.md:8:# IDENTITY.md - Agent Identity\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.dev.md:8:# SOUL.md - The Soul of C-3PO\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/USER.dev.md:8:# USER.md - User Profile\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:2:title: \"SOUL.md Template\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:3:summary: \"Workspace template for SOUL.md\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/SOUL.md:8:# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.md:7:# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/IDENTITY.md:28:- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:2:summary: \"Dev agent AGENTS.md (C-3PO)\"\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:8:# AGENTS.md - OpenClaw Workspace\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:15:- Your agent identity lives in IDENTITY.md.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:16:- Your profile lives in USER.md.\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/templates/AGENTS.dev.md:25:git add AGENTS.md\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib