{"type":"message","id":"377452e3","parentId":"72c2e4b3","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:56:56.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, I see! The \"HEARTBEAT.md\" matches are mostly the heartbeat POLL messages (the user prompts), not the actual file content. Only msg_id=6 is the actual HEARTBEAT.md file content.\n\nAnd SOUL.md full content only appears once (msg_id=323). Let me check if the bootstrap files are being duplicated or if they're only stored once. It seems like LCM might already be deduplicating or the bootstrap files are only injected once per session.\n\nLet me check all the bootstrap files more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Clarification:** The \"HEARTBEAT.md\" matches are mostly **heartbeat poll prompts** (not the file content).\n\nLet me check the actual bootstrap file content:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d25085e161b249c89a51502f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst { DatabaseSync } = require('node:sqlite');\nconst db = new DatabaseSync('/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/lcm.db');\n\nconst files = [\n  ['SOUL.md', '# SOUL.md - Who You Are'],\n  ['AGENTS.md', '# AGENTS.md - Your Workspace'],\n  ['IDENTITY.md', '# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?'],\n  ['USER.md', '# USER.md - About Your Human'],\n  ['HEARTBEAT.md', '# HEARTBEAT.md - Free Mind Protocol'],\n  ['MEMORY.md', '# MEMORY.md - Long-Term Memory']\n];\n\nconsole.log('Bootstrap file content in LCM:\\\\n');\n\nfor (const [name, header] of files) {\n  const result = db.prepare(\\`\n    SELECT message_id, seq, role, LENGTH(content) as len, created_at\n    FROM messages\n    WHERE content LIKE ?\n    ORDER BY message_id\n  \\`).all(header + '%');\n  \n  console.log(\\`\\${name}: \\${result.length} occurrence(s)\\`);\n  if (result.length > 0) {\n    result.forEach((r, i) => {\n      console.log(\\`  \\${i+1}. msg_id=\\${r.message_id}, seq=\\${r.seq}, len=\\${r.len}, \\${r.created_at}\\`);\n    });\n  }\n  console.log('');\n}\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":51615,"output":497,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773539804431}}
