{"type":"message","id":"8ee52d1e","parentId":"449a0caa","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:57:22.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Very interesting! I see:\n\n1. The message 323 is a grep result from token-use.md that mentions bootstrap files - not the actual bootstrap file content\n2. The message_parts table shows detailed message parts including reasoning, compaction events, etc.\n3. There was a compaction event: \"LCM compaction leaf pass (normal): 129870 -> 114292\" - this means compaction already happened!\n4. The bootstrap files (SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, etc.) are NOT being duplicated in the database\n\nWait - the earlier search showed HEARTBEAT.md had 1 occurrence. But the message_parts show there's already been compaction. Let me check if the bootstrap files were compacted into summaries.\n\nLet me check the summaries table to see if bootstrap files were compacted.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Interesting findings:**\n\n1. **LCM already compacted:** `129,870 → 114,292 tokens` (leaf pass)\n2. **Bootstrap files NOT directly in messages table** — only HEARTBEAT.md appears once\n3. **Message 323** is a grep result, not the actual file\n\nLet me check if bootstrap files were compacted into **summaries**:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_675ec1e0432b432ca2fc281a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst { DatabaseSync } = require('node:sqlite');\nconst db = new DatabaseSync('/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/lcm.db');\n\n// Check summaries table\nconst summaries = db.prepare('SELECT summary_id, kind, depth, LENGTH(content) as len, substr(content, 1, 200) as preview FROM summaries ORDER BY summary_id').all();\nconsole.log('Summaries:', summaries.length);\nsummaries.forEach((s, i) => {\n  console.log(\\`\\\\n\\${i+1}. \\${s.summary_id} (\\${s.kind}, depth=\\${s.depth}, len=\\${s.len})\\`);\n  console.log(\\`   Preview: \\${s.preview.substring(0, 150)}...\\`);\n});\n\n// Check context_items for what's in the context\nconst items = db.prepare(\\`\n  SELECT ci.ordinal, ci.item_type, \n         CASE WHEN ci.item_type = 'message' THEN m.message_id ELSE s.summary_id END as id\n  FROM context_items ci\n  LEFT JOIN messages m ON ci.message_id = m.message_id\n  LEFT JOIN summaries s ON ci.summary_id = s.summary_id\n  ORDER BY ci.ordinal\n\\`).all();\nconsole.log('\\\\n\\\\nContext items:', items.length);\nitems.forEach((item, i) => {\n  console.log(\\`  \\${i+1}. ordinal=\\${item.ordinal}, type=\\${item.item_type}, id=\\${item.id}\\`);\n});\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":56864,"output":657,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773539827429}}
