{"type":"message","id":"f4e19e19","parentId":"73aeab04","timestamp":"2026-03-15T02:52:15.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the comment is added to the PR. Now let me:\n1. Copy the updated engine.ts to the installed extension\n2. Update the TODO.md to mark the preserve tag task as complete\n3. Update daily notes\n4. Let Allan know the LCM code is done\n\nActually, I already copied the engine.ts earlier, but let me make sure the installed extension has the latest version with my changes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good, PR updated. Let me make sure the installed extension has the latest code and update the TODO."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b46e4d8db5a446d2becff853","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/lossless-claw/src/engine.ts /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/extensions/lossless-claw/src/engine.ts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":50166,"output":190,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773543117960}}
