{"type":"message","id":"47625a64","parentId":"8a5f1de8","timestamp":"2026-03-15T02:55:40.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the branch is pushed. Now let me create a new PR.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Good, pushed. Now let me create a new PR."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ca9868cc1f34a28a8d9cf9f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/lossless-claw && gh pr create --repo Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw --title \"feat: add preserve tag support for bootstrap files\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\n\nAdd support for `<!-- preserve -->...<!-- /preserve -->` tags to prevent certain content from being ingested into the LCM database.\n\n## Motivation\n\nBootstrap files (SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, etc.) are injected fresh each turn by the host system (OpenClaw). Without this feature, the same content would be duplicated in the context on every turn, eventually getting compacted into summaries and potentially lost or distorted.\n\n## Implementation\n\n- Add preserve tag detection in `ingestSingle()` method\n- Content wrapped with `<!-- preserve -->...<!-- /preserve -->` tags is skipped during ingest\n- Support optional type suffix: `<!-- preserve:soul -->` (ignored but allowed for documentation)\n- Tag format is intentionally generic (not LCM-specific) so any context engine implementation can respect it\n\n## Test Plan\n\nAdded 3 tests:\n1. `skips preserve-tagged content in ingest` - verifies content is not ingested\n2. `skips preserve-tagged content with optional type suffix` - verifies suffix support\n3. `ingests content without preserve tags normally` - verifies normal content still works\n\nAll 250 tests pass.\n\n## Usage Example\n\nIn OpenClaw, bootstrap files would be wrapped like:\n\n\\`\\`\\`\n<!-- preserve:soul -->\n# SOUL.md\n\nYour soul content here...\n\n<!-- /preserve -->\n\\`\\`\\`\n\nThis ensures identity-critical content stays fresh each turn without polluting the context database.\nEOF\n)\" --head archeren:preserve-tag-clean --base main 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":53262,"output":414,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773543323150}}
