{"type":"message","id":"7bb11f2d","parentId":"aecae5fc","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:36:16.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. According to HEARTBEAT.md, I should:\n1. Check TODO.md first\n2. If working, reply with ONE sentence about what I'm working on\n3. Record events from last 15 minutes to memory/daily/\n\nI was explaining the assemble phase to Allan and checking how OpenClaw integrates with LCM's assemble phase. I need to understand if OpenClaw injects bootstrap files independently of LCM or if LCM's assemble controls the final context.\n\nLet me reply with a one-sentence status and update the daily notes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Investigating how OpenClaw integrates with LCM's assemble phase - checking if bootstrap files are injected independently."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c277bff454d48068bd8a094","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-15.md","limit":50,"offset":1}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":45474,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773545761100}}
