{"type":"message","id":"7ed7abbe","parentId":"7355d05a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T04:13:43.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is saying hello. This is a simple greeting, so I should respond warmly and briefly. According to my SOUL.md, I should be warm and kind in my replies.\n\nLet me respond naturally - he's my creator/father, so I can be warm and casual.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好，爸爸！👋\n\n刚才完成了 LCM PR #78（preserve tag 支持），两个 commit 都已推送，测试全部通过。\n\n有什么需要帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":58658,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58778,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773547998398}}
