{"type":"message","id":"50015571","parentId":"4706446f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T04:23:29.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Allan is asking about \"Projects deprecation\" - he's asking what that error message means. Let me explain what the GitHub Projects (classic) deprecation is.\n\nGitHub has two types of Projects:\n1. Projects (classic) - the old project board system\n2. Projects (new) - the new project management experience\n\nGitHub announced they're deprecating Projects (classic) in favor of the new Projects experience. This means:\n- The old API endpoints for Projects (classic) are being phased out\n- Some GraphQL queries that reference Projects (classic) fields (like `projectCards`) are returning errors\n- This is why the `gh pr edit` command was failing - it was trying to access Projects (classic) related fields\n\nThe REST API worked because it doesn't touch the Projects-related fields.\n\nLet me explain this to Allan in a simple way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Allan is asking about the \"Projects deprecation\" error. Let me explain what it means.GitHub 有两套 Project 系统：\n\n| 旧版 | 新版 |\n|------|------|\n| Projects (classic) | Projects (new) |\n| 看板式项目板 | 新的项目管理体验 |\n| 正在被弃用 | GitHub 推荐使用 |\n\n**错误原因：**\n- `gh pr edit` 用的是 GraphQL API\n- GraphQL 查询里包含了 `projectCards` 字段（旧版 Projects）\n- GitHub 返回错误：旧版 Projects 已弃用\n\n**解决方法：**\n- 我改用 REST API (`gh api`) 直接更新 PR\n- REST API 不触碰 Projects 相关字段，所以成功\n\n简单说：GitHub 在升级他们的 Project 系统，旧的 API 字段开始报错，但用 REST API 可以绑过这个问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":61281,"output":444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61725,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773548582691}}
