{"type":"message","id":"23f1e41b","parentId":"788fcdb9","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:21:16.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand. The skill structure is:\n\n```\nskills/\n├── skill-name/\n│   ├── SKILL.md (required)\n│   ├── scripts/ (optional)\n│   ├── references/ (optional)\n│   └── assets/ (optional)\n```\n\nSo yes, Allan is right - you create a skill folder, and put everything under that folder. Let me confirm this with him.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"是的，你说的对！结构是：\n\n```\nskills/\n├── skill-name/           ← 技能文件夹\n│   ├── SKILL.md          ← 必需\n│   ├── scripts/          ← 可选\n│   │   └── *.py\n│   ├── references/       ← 可选\n│   │   └── *.md\n│   └── assets/           ← 可选\n│       └── templates/\n```\n\n**每个技能是一个文件夹**，SKILL.md 放在文件夹根目录。\n\n示例：\n```\nskills/\n├── skill-creator/\n│   ├── SKILL.md\n│   └── scripts/\n│       ├── init_skill.py\n│       └── package_skill.py\n├── github/\n│   └── SKILL.md\n└── weather/\n    └── SKILL.md\n```\n\n创建新技能的命令：\n```bash\nscripts/init_skill.py my-skill --path /path/to/skills/\n```\n\n这会自动创建 `my-skill/` 文件夹和 SKILL.md 模板。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":125816,"output":356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773551999804}}
