{"type":"message","id":"ac846220","parentId":"5ec5ac7a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:25:15.134Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_03aa9c19e3814addad4b23dd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-wiki\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":118,"aggregated":"/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-wiki\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-perm\n/home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc","cwd":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773552315104}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a499470","parentId":"ac846220","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:25:55.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The feishu skills are under extensions/feishu/skills/. There are multiple feishu skills:\n- feishu-wiki\n- feishu-drive\n- feishu-perm\n- feishu-doc\n\nThe feishu_api.md is a general API reference file. I should check what's in it and then decide where to put it. Maybe it should go in a references folder under one of these skills, or maybe it should be a separate feishu-api skill, or maybe it should go in a shared location.\n\nLet me first read the file to understand its content.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc1b0701ea5a4441b4c48262","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/tools/feishu_api.md","limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":126459,"output":214,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773552315127}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fc39a5a","parentId":"2a499470","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:25:55.063Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fc1b0701ea5a4441b4c48262","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Feishu API Reference\n\n## Authentication\n\nGet tenant access token:\n\n```bash\nTOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"app_id\":\"YOUR_APP_ID\",\"app_secret\":\"YOUR_APP_SECRET\"}' | jq -r '.tenant_access_token')\n```\n\n**App ID**: stored in `openclaw.json` under `channels.feishu.appId`\n**App Secret**: stored in `openclaw.json` under `channels.feishu.appSecret`\n\n---\n\n## Image Messaging\n\n### Process: Send Image to User\n\n1. **Upload image** → get `image_key`\n2. **Send message** with `msg_type: \"image\"` and `content: {\"image_key\": \"...\"}`\n\n### Step 1: Upload Image\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/images' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -F 'image_type=message' \\\n  -F 'image=@/path/to/image.png' | jq .\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 0,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"image_key\": \"img_v3_02vi_xxxxx\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Step 2: Send Image Message\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n\n[211 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773552355033}}
{"type":"message","id":"88d688f2","parentId":"7fc39a5a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T05:26:33.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a general Feishu API reference that covers:\n- Authentication\n- Image messaging\n- Document editing\n- Comment API\n\nIt seems like it should be a references file. Since there are multiple feishu skills (feishu-doc, feishu-wiki, feishu-drive, feishu-perm), I should probably put this in a common location. \n\nLooking at the skill structure, I could:\n1. Create a `references/` folder under one of the existing feishu skills\n2. Create a new `feishu-api` skill with this as a reference\n3. Put it in the feishu extension folder as a shared reference\n\nActually, looking at the available_skills section in the system prompt, I see these feishu skills:\n- feishu-doc - \"Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\"\n- feishu-drive - \"Feishu cloud storage file management. Activate when user mentions cloud space, folders, drive.\"\n- feishu-perm - \"Feishu permission management for documents and files. Activate when user mentions sharing, permissions, collaborators.\"\n- feishu-wiki - \"Feishu knowledge base navigation. Activate when user mentions knowledge base, wiki, or wiki links.\"\n\nThe feishu_api.md contains general API information that could be useful for all of these. Maybe I should put it in the feishu extension folder, or create a references folder that all feishu skills can access.\n\nActually, looking at the skill-creator documentation, references should be inside a specific skill folder. Since this is general API documentation, maybe it should go in a new skill or be distributed to each skill that needs it.\n\nLet me check if there's a main feishu skill or if I should create one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_809061c156054c1cb36b781c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/ubuntu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":126272,"output":582,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773552355057}}
