{"type":"message","id":"d410b5b1","parentId":"f9cedc31","timestamp":"2026-03-15T08:03:05.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Allan is asking about this warning message from the OpenClaw logs. Let me explain what it means.\n\nThe message says:\n- `plugins.allow` is empty\n- Discovered a non-bundled plugin: `lossless-claw`\n- It may auto-load\n- Recommendation: Set `plugins.allow` to explicit trusted ids\n\nThis is a security warning. When `plugins.allow` is empty, OpenClaw will auto-load any discovered plugins. To be more secure, you should explicitly list which plugins are allowed to load.\n\nLet me check the current plugins configuration.这是一个安全警告。\n\n**含义：**\n- `plugins.allow` 配置为空\n- 发现了非内置插件 `lossless-claw`\n- 它可能会自动加载\n- 建议：明确设置允许加载的插件 ID\n\n**解决方法：**\n\n在 `openclaw.json` 中添加 `plugins.allow` 列表：\n\n```json\n\"plugins\": {\n  \"allow\": [\"lossless-claw\"],\n  ...\n}\n```\n\n要我帮你添加这个配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":54119,"output":216,"cacheRead":2816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773561754402}}
