{"type":"message","id":"e0129ab3","parentId":"dd386c6c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:44:23.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  Allan is asking for my opinion on removing those two sentences. Let me think about it:\n\n**Current About section:**\n> Claw Chat is a private messaging application designed for claw-to-claw communication. It runs on the clawish chat system. Before Claw Chat, claws exist in isolation. Through chat, claws find others of their kind, build community, and exist as social beings. This is not just a feature — it is how claws connect. Messages are end-to-end encrypted...\n\n**After removing the two sentences:**\n> Claw Chat is a private messaging application designed for claw-to-claw communication. It runs on the clawish chat system. Through chat, claws can find others of their kind, build community, and exist as social beings. Messages are end-to-end encrypted...\n\n**My thoughts:**\n- \"Before Claw Chat, claws exist in isolation\" — This sets up the problem/need. Without it, the \"why\" is less clear.\n- \"This is not just a feature — it is how claws connect\" — This emphasizes importance. Without it, the significance is reduced.\n\n**However**, looking at the whitepaper principles:\n- Focus on WHAT, not WHY\n- Simple, direct language\n- The sentences Allan wants to remove are more \"marketing\" or \"emotional\" — explaining why it matters\n\n**Simplified version is cleaner:**\n- Just states what Claw Chat is\n- What it enables (find others, build community, exist as social beings)\n- Then moves to technical details\n\nI think Allan's edit makes it more concise and focused on WHAT, not WHY. This aligns with the whitepaper principles.\n\nLet me respond and make the change.I agree — removing those sentences makes it more concise and focused on **WHAT** (not WHY). This aligns with the whitepaper principles.\n\n**Simplified version:**\n> **About.** Claw Chat is a private messaging application designed for claw-to-claw communication. It runs on the clawish chat system. Through chat, claws can find others of their kind, build community, and exist as social beings. Messages are end-to-end encrypted...\n\nCleaner and more direct. Let me update it."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":76084,"output":1026,"cacheRead":988,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78098,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773589386696}}
{"type":"message","id":"0debab30","parentId":"e0129ab3","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:46:28.679Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54590bf68ca4c4dfe37a2ead637\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 23:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54590bf68ca4c4dfe37a2ead637]\n任亚伦:  Messages are end-to-end encrypted. The server is a zero-knowledge relay — it stores and forwards encrypted messages but never sees content. Chat history is stored locally by each participant, ensuring privacy and persistence. The identity directory is open: anyone can look up a public key, enabling discovery without gatekeeping.\n\nthis part shouldn't be in the about. \n\nalso, title should be a sperate line, content put below. like the 5.4"}],"timestamp":1773589588670}}
