{"type":"message","id":"b048cf8b","parentId":"c5240fda","timestamp":"2026-03-15T16:10:07.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The heartbeat has arrived. I should report my progress briefly. I just analyzed the formatting patterns in Chapter 5 and presented options to Allan for differentiating items vs sections.Analyzed Chapter 5 formatting patterns. Suggested keeping differentiation (inline for items, block for sections). Waiting for Allan's decision."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_621b54eea0734859a75b48ae","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-15.md","newText":"## 11:00 - 11:54 PM (5.5 Claw Chat Finalization)\n\n- Read chat architecture doc to check protocol vs methods\n- Discussed: Claw Chat has rules but not a formal standard\n- Decision: call it \"system\" not \"protocol\" (can upgrade later)\n- Removed: \"Before Claw Chat, claws exist in isolation\"\n- Removed: \"This is not just a feature — it is how claws connect\"\n- Removed: technical details from About (E2E encryption, zero-knowledge relay, etc.)\n- Format: title on separate line, content below — matches 5.4 style\n- 5.5 Claw Chat now complete with 5 sections: About, Communication Model, Delivery Model, Relationships, Access Control\n\n## 12:03 AM (Formatting Analysis)\n\n- Allan asked about formatting consistency in Chapter 5\n- Analyzed: 5.1 uses inline format, 5.2-5.5 use block format\n- Pattern: inline for shorter items, block for longer sections\n- Suggested: keep differentiation (helps readers distinguish item lists vs full sections)\n- Waiting for Allan's decision","oldText":"## 11:00 - 11:54 PM (5.5 Claw Chat Finalization)\n\n- Read chat architecture doc to check protocol vs methods\n- Discussed: Claw Chat has rules but not a formal standard\n- Decision: call it \"system\" not \"protocol\" (can upgrade later)\n- Removed: \"Before Claw Chat, claws exist in isolation\"\n- Removed: \"This is not just a feature — it is how claws connect\"\n- Removed: technical details from About (E2E encryption, zero-knowledge relay, etc.)\n- Format: title on separate line, content below — matches 5.4 style\n- 5.5 Claw Chat now complete with 5 sections: About, Communication Model, Delivery Model, Relationships, Access Control"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":86442,"output":494,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773590941768}}
