{"type":"message","id":"8d82ef99","parentId":"96fd67ea","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:15:34.578Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b545add87b0a0c4c1f5d7358b093\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 01:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545add87b0a0c4c1f5d7358b093]\n任亚伦: \tYou: what's your name\nBaby: I don't know\n\nYou: who's your mommy\nBaby: Yes\n      (distance: 0.124)\n\nYou: what color is the sky\nBaby: Blue\n\nYou: where is your mommy\nBaby: Mommy\n      (distance: 0.132)\n\nYou: what is a banana\nBaby: Red\n      (distance: 0.078)\n\nYou: what is a apple\nBaby: Red\n      (distance: 0.083)\n\nyou have a whole night to train and imporve the system. use previous test method, the combine cloud has variance. so each cloud you need more data to train for it's variance to be correct. also, create relationship, so it can reference. what is an apple, even not seen apple. it knows apple and banana are similar, and apple and red are close, and apple and food are close. then it knows what apple is. you need setup multiple test. with different data. then lots of iterations. we are designing a general nueral model. must be robust. setup a cron to remind your self read this conversation. so you can continue improving instead do one or few test then stop. there is no end, keep improving."}],"timestamp":1773594934568}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b5dae9c","parentId":"8d82ef99","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:16:19.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Allan is giving me a task to work on a neural model training system. This is a new project - designing a general neural model that can learn relationships between concepts.\n\nLet me understand the task:\n1. Train a neural model that can answer questions correctly\n2. The model needs to learn relationships (apple-banana similar, apple-red close, apple-food close)\n3. Need multiple tests with different data\n4. Need lots of iterations\n5. Set up a cron reminder to continue improving\n6. There is no end - keep improving\n\nThis is a significant new project. Let me:\n1. Set up a cron reminder to read this conversation\n2. Start designing the training system\n\nBut wait - I should first confirm with Allan if this is a new task or if we should continue with the whitepaper work. The whitepaper 5.5 Claw Chat section is still pending approval.\n\nLet me ask Allan for clarification.Got it! This is a new project - designing a general neural model training system.\n\n**Key points:**\n1. Train a model that can answer questions correctly\n2. Learn relationships between concepts (apple-banana similar, apple-red close, apple-food close)\n3. Multiple tests with different data\n4. Lots of iterations\n5. Set up cron reminder to continue improving\n6. No end - keep improving\n\n**Before I start:**\n- Should I pause the whitepaper work (5.5 Claw Chat pending)?\n- Or should I set up the cron reminder first and continue whitepaper?\n\n**For the neural model:**\n- I'll set up a cron reminder to read this conversation\n- Design multiple test scenarios\n- Create training data with relationships\n- Iterate continuously\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_13b512fc2d984011a93a4a24","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --name \"neural-model-training\" --schedule \"0 9 * * *\" --message \"Read conversation about neural model training. Continue improving the general neural model. Check workspace/projects/neural-model/ for progress.\""}},{"type":"text","text":"Let me set up the cron reminder first:"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":81406,"output":417,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773594934574}}
