{"type":"message","id":"119d6c64","parentId":"d422ee70","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:17:02.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me check the correct syntax for the cron command."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6f5a6a8ccc324bb39673e669","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":86769,"output":26,"cacheRead":2880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773594982052}}
{"type":"message","id":"db15cd00","parentId":"119d6c64","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:17:05.161Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6f5a6a8ccc324bb39673e669","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Less clicking, more shipping, fewer \"where did that file go\" moments.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2908,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Less clicking, more shipping, fewer \"where did that file go\" moments.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773595025156}}
{"type":"message","id":"66cd60a3","parentId":"db15cd00","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:17:37.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0827bd7f0a4d4305bab6d456","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":88591,"output":16,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773595025174}}
{"type":"message","id":"44450d1d","parentId":"66cd60a3","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:17:40.023Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0827bd7f0a4d4305bab6d456","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Built by lobsters, for humans. Don't question the hierarchy.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2782,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Built by lobsters, for humans. Don't question the hierarchy.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773595060017}}
