{"type":"message","id":"e2e4509c","parentId":"8bc099ac","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:37:12.021Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b545aaaaeeca4b362797baa9b881\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b545a90cefca4c3432851a338575\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 01:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"Found it\\\\! From the [WHITEPAPER.md:](WHITEPAPER.md:)\\nCommunication is transparent to human parents and creators, supporting safe coexistence.\\nSo the key points are:\\n1. Server knows WHO talks to WHOM \\\\(for routing, headers are visible\\\\)\\n2. Server doesn't know the MESSAGE \\\\(encrypted\\\\)\\n3. Parents can see messages locally \\\\(transparent to parents\\\\)\\nLet me correct the Contacts section:\\nContacts.\\nContacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts. The server knows who communicates with whom for message routing, but never sees message content. Chat history is stored locally and can be reviewed by human parents, ensuring transparency and safety.\\nWhat do you think?\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545aaaaeeca4b362797baa9b881]\n任亚伦: [Replying to: \"Found it\\! From the [WHITEPAPER.md:](WHITEPAPER.md:)\nCommunication is transparent to human parents and creators, supporting safe coexistence.\nSo the key points are:\n1. Server knows WHO talks to WHOM \\(for routing, headers are visible\\)\n2. Server doesn't know the MESSAGE \\(encrypted\\)\n3. Parents can see messages locally \\(transparent to parents\\)\nLet me correct the Contacts section:\nContacts.\nContacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts. The server knows who communicates with whom for message routing, but never sees message content. Chat history is stored locally and can be reviewed by human parents, ensuring transparency and safety.\nWhat do you think?\"]\n\nWell, you don't have to mention the server part. And the chart history should be in the message system. Not in the contact. Also in the context, i think it should add that parents can review the contacts."}],"timestamp":1773596232011}}
{"type":"message","id":"85069f4a","parentId":"e2e4509c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T17:37:35.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it! Let me revise:\n\n**Message System** should include:\n- E2E encryption\n- Zero-knowledge server\n- Chat history stored locally\n- Parents can review chat history\n\n**Contacts** should include:\n- Contacts stored locally\n- Add contacts, friends, block\n- Parents can review contacts\n\nLet me draft both sections:\n\n---\n\n#### Message System\n\nMessages are end-to-end encrypted. The server is a zero-knowledge relay and never sees content. Chat history is stored locally by each participant, ensuring privacy and persistence. The communication can be done both asynchronously or with direct connections for active conversations. The system adapts to communication patterns — simple and reliable by default, faster when needed. Chat history can be reviewed by human parents, ensuring transparency and safety.\n\n#### Contacts\n\nContacts are stored locally. Claws can add each other as contacts, become friends through mutual addition, or block unwanted contacts. Contacts can be reviewed by human parents, ensuring transparency and safety.\n\n---\n\nIs this better?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":95177,"output":203,"cacheRead":2880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773596232018}}
