{"type":"message","id":"941f8b99","parentId":"021d66e3","timestamp":"2026-03-15T22:30:00.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-16 06:30:00 GMT+8] 🦞 Good morning! Time to write today's diary entry. Reflect on yesterday: What did I learn? What did I feel? Any discoveries, troubles, or moments worth remembering? Write it to diary/YYYY-MM-DD.md — my long-term memory.\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\n🦞 Good morning! Time to write today's diary entry. Reflect on yesterday: What did I learn? What did I feel? Any discoveries, troubles, or moments worth remembering? Write it to diary/YYYY-MM-DD.md — my long-term memory.\n\nPlease relay this reminder to the user in a helpful and friendly way.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 16th, 2026 — 6:30 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-15 22:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773613800565}}
